title: Ep46 Gossip at the Corpse Cart
description:
This month's GACC is full of Spanish meats, a really big pumpkin, blessed shapewear, bone sugar, a preserved clown, and lots of poop. Tune in for October's Gossip at the Corpse Cart!

For a full list of show sponsors, visit https://wineandcrimepodcast.com/sponsors/
